c: 26
v: 227
t: "Yallal yeemeneeh meqe tamoomi abbaasiteeh Yalla maggom cuseeh yundullumeeniik gamadal Rasuul kee islaam diinik kalalak koros gadabal yab gacsa mara akke waytek. isi nafsii kee seehada yudlume mari aaxige-le kah gacoonu waan gacim kinni gacim rabaak lakal, diggah usuk uma gacim kinni"